    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182990/extras/bcf575f0468a8d884c6767c46e95e52c.avif?t=1755193486\" width=600 height=124 /></span>Freelance hacker Quei-Li is given a new job: uncover information from the Allocated Reality Institute (ARI) about a high-profile corruption case. While she typically avoids high-risk jobs like this, her curiosity about the secret files and her wish to bring on positive change to Shiba Island convinces her to accept. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The job leads to Quei-Li bluffing her way into the ARI as an undercover programmer. She builds up a rapport with her coworkers while seeking the information her client needs. The more she digs around, the more secrets Quei-Li discovers, leading her to question her own existence. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2182990/extras/062aca9002b5d73caadd8bb0a4708e21.avif?t=1755193486\" width=600 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose wisely</strong> - help Quei-Li navigate her undercover job. Will she succeed in retrieving the classified data?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple endings</strong> - what seems like a good outcome might cause someone else to suffer. Your choices impact the endings!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Original character artwork</strong> - Alicia García Ochoa's dog illustrations make the inhabitants of Shiba Inu Island come to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hacking mini-game</strong> - step into Quei-Li's role with a brain-twisting hacking mini-game! (The mini-game is completely optional) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Accessibility options</strong> - tune your experience and comfort while enjoying the game. Toggle between 4k resolution and full HD resolution. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Autumn with the Shiba Inu is set in the same universe as the first game in the Shiba Inu series, A Summer with the Shiba Inu. &quot;Autumn&quot; is a standalone story, so reading &quot;Summer&quot; is not required to enjoy Autumn with the Shiba Inu! </p>",
